# admin-api 用户资料与社交（profile.api → user.rpc/Identity + screenplay.rpc）
@gateway = http://192.168.110.167:8888/
@adminUsername = admin
@adminPassword = admin123


### BEGIN GENERATED

### @name login
POST {{gateway}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "{{adminUsername}}",
  "password": "{{adminPassword}}"
}

> {%
  client.global.set("accessToken", response.body.data.access_token);
%}

### @name getProfile
GET {{gateway}}/api/admin/profile
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Accept: application/json

### @name updateProfile
PUT {{gateway}}/api/admin/profile
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "nickname": "示例用户",
  "email": "user@example.com",
  "phone": "13800000000",
  "avatar": "example"
}
### @name getPublicUserProfile
GET {{gateway}}/api/admin/social/users/{{id}}/public
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Accept: application/json

### @name followUser
POST {{gateway}}/api/admin/social/users/{{id}}/follow
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}


### @name unfollowUser
DELETE {{gateway}}/api/admin/social/users/{{id}}/follow
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Accept: application/json

### @name listUserScreenplays
GET {{gateway}}/api/admin/social/users/{{id}}/screenplays?page=1&page_size=20
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Accept: application/json

### END GENERATED



